==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sennet
<hw>Sen"net</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Properly, a sign
given for the entrance or exit of actors, from OF. <ets>sinet</ets>,
<ets>signet</ets>, dim. of <ets>signe</ets>. See <er>Signet</er>.]</ety>
<def>A signal call on a trumpet or cornet for entrance or exit on the
stage.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sennet</ent>⟦br⟧

